cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM

The paper deals with computer vision techniques for detecting and classifying exudates in diabetic retinopathy images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also makes use of machine learning techniques such as support vector machines, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves mathematical morphology, which could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper deals with medical imaging, which could also place it in cs.MM (Multimedia).
